ShakeSmartphone is an application for Logging the accelerometer and gyroscope sensor data of smartphone when shaking the smartphone.
There are 12 shaking methods. And user needs to follow.
However, you can ignore them, and just log accelerometer and gyroscope sensor data whenever you want.
Just with START and STOP.
The data will be saved as .txt format in Log folder in sdcard.
This is written in Android Eclipse not in Android Studio. 
